{"tid":1509403,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我愛這個國，可誰愛我呢？","createTime":"2019-08-26T23:41:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T00:37:07.000Z","uid":204486,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"dfe9860c6130d34d648e9aef52639f18a223c341","tid":1509403,"uid":204486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T23:41:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/wRO0tae5u5E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FwRO0tae5u5E&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQroeonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=f589cd24\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/wRO0tae5u5E</a><br />\n<br />\n最近睇Youtube成日都會彈啲政治片出嚟<br />\n<br />\n本身都唔會撳入去睇，因為八成係啲深藍片<br />\n<br />\n諗住入去report下啲五毛<br />\n等佢哋繼續享受国內嘅言論自由<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後睇啲留言雖然簡體，但好多正常人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ix4WU2T.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fix4WU2T.png&h=2263fefe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7afOL9z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7afOL9z.png&h=8c066957&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁就好好奇去睇<br />\n<br />\n套戲講緊嘅同而家發生緊嘅好相似<br />\n<br />\n例如罷課遊行，畀人話係暴動<br />\n<br />\n之後佢一邊講一邊串而家班中国小粉紅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n揸住跑車講粗口，收錢打學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇完只可以講 奴性呢樣嘢真係天生<br />\n<br />\n清朝係咁，到今時今日都係咁<br />\n<br />\n見到中国牆內仲有啲正常人，<br />\n<br />\n就真係唔撚明班藍絲，點解都係未醒覺<br />\n<br />\n我已經send咗俾我個班藍絲屋企人<br />\n睇下佢咁愛国有咩感想<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbc4e01bfc007b14ca9d7730e3ebe9322998e63c","tid":1509403,"uid":33930,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T23:41:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9hjf7rg.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9hjf7rg.gif&h=994c84f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQroeonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=0b4f894e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQroeonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=624fdce2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQroeonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=954f3127\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"487a88e2848d606b50b4e21f455279219acda19a","tid":1509403,"uid":204486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T23:42:35.000Z","msg":"五毛打人出處原來都係呢套戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94fd8f1bf7c6c4d7eb1067d7bb49f6a564e020b9","tid":1509403,"uid":190858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T23:42:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>有用請幫推</strong><br />\n<br />\n[核彈文宣]828#ProtestToo集會全世界都要去 平權=反極權 將火源燒開去</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1508048\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1508048</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RdRycGF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRdRycGF.jpg&h=676fb912&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KitHQtm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKitHQtm.jpg&h=29e92096&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"86ef9059e9082ce2000fd53f4ecf874ad69b6327","tid":1509403,"uid":204486,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T23:43:56.000Z","msg":"希望繼續輸出